trans-unit.target: Ofrece compatibilidad en tiempo de diseño para los controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart" />.

<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner> proporciona compatibilidad en tiempo de diseño <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> controles.

trans-unit.source: It extends its parent class, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner>, by adding a control-specific <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Extiende su clase primaria, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner>, mediante la adición de un determinado control <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> a la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> colección.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner> does not render the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner> no se representará asociado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> control en la superficie de diseño.

trans-unit.source: The associated control, <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart" />, is a <see langword="sealed" /> class and cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: El control asociado, <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart" />, es un <see langword="sealed" /> clase y no puede heredarse.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, there is little value in deriving from <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner" /> because it cannot be overridden to apply to any other control.
trans-unit.target: Por lo tanto, no tienen poco valor deriva <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner" /> porque no se puede invalidar para aplicar a cualquier otro control.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the parent method to prevent rendering of the control.
trans-unit.target: Reemplaza el método primario para evitar la representación del control.

trans-unit.source: Either an empty string ("") or the value of <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml" />.
trans-unit.target: O una cadena vacía ("") o el valor de <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml" />.

trans-unit.source: If there is no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart.WebPartsTemplate%2A> associated with the control, the designer displays the standard gray box with the class name and instance name of the control.
trans-unit.target: Si no hay ningún <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart.WebPartsTemplate%2A> asociado al control, el diseñador muestra el cuadro estándar gris con el nombre de clase y el nombre de la instancia del control.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, no design-time rendering occurs at all because the check boxes and Web Parts titles are rendered by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome> instead of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> itself.
trans-unit.target: En caso contrario, tiempo de diseño se produce ninguna representación en absoluto porque las casillas de verificación y los títulos de elementos Web se representan mediante la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome> en lugar de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> propio.

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup to represent an empty control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el marcado para representar un control vacío en la superficie del diseño.

trans-unit.source: This operation renders the control as a gray box showing the class name and the instance name.
trans-unit.target: Esta operación representa el control como un cuadro gris que muestra el nombre de clase y el nombre de instancia.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart" /> control associated with the designer.

Binds the designer to the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart" /> control and sets the <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewFlags.TemplateEditing" /> view flag to <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: Enlaza el diseñador al control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart" /> asociado y establece el marcador de vista <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewFlags.TemplateEditing" /> en <see langword="true" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of template groups, each containing one or more template definitions.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene una colección de grupos de plantillas, cada una con una o varias definiciones de plantilla.

trans-unit.source: The appended <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection" /> associated with this class.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> property overrides its base implementation to add a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> object that is specific to this class.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> propiedad invalida su implementación base para agregar un <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> objeto que es específico para esta clase.
